beer.beer_name: Special Batch: Superdelic Hazy Pale Ale
beer.beer_description: Brewed exclusively for Beer Cartel's 2024 Advent Calendar, Superdelic Hazy Pale Ale is a whirlwind of a trans-pacific hop adventure, with NZ Superdelic, Motueka, and Nelson Sauvin dancing up front with some American Citra hops. A rounded malt profile makes way for a smooth and clean finish, pairs well with pomme noisettes. ]
